Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.53,0:00:08.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What time does the competition start?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.33,0:00:12.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...the doors open at 3:00...\Nand the thing starts at 3:30.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.79,0:00:14.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's 3:20 now!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.38,0:00:16.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Crap! It's just about to start!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.09,0:00:18.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No worries, no worries.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.17,0:00:20.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fourth anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.17,0:00:20.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.09,0:00:22.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's cutting it close!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.70,0:02:08.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5}Main Hall - Information
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.57,0:02:12.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're here! Just made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.33,0:02:15.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I got us programs.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.62,0:02:16.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.48,0:02:18.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No. 11 was last year's Honorable Mention, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.58,0:02:20.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What about the Audience Award?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.46,0:02:21.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if she'll be able to play well?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.92,0:02:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That Mr. Kazama's leading the judging panel, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.59,0:02:26.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a good chance to catch his eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.34,0:02:30.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You know what, it's like a different dimension\Nin here. Everyone here's like a celebrity.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.68,0:02:33.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This tension before the competition\Nstarts is the same everywhere, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.85,0:02:35.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even I'm starting to get nervous!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.39,0:02:37.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're not even competing, Tsubaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.65,0:02:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.11,0:02:42.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Since I'm going this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.98,0:02:44.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.19,0:02:46.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be rooting for you, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.19,0:02:47.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! I'll do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.24,0:02:51.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The auditorium's this way, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.16,0:02:52.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.17,0:03:05.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.17,0:03:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,N-No...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.80,0:03:09.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.34,0:03:12.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is your workplace.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.19,0:03:26.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Towa Music Competition Committee Sponsor\NSecond Annual Towa Music Competition\NViolin - Middle School Division
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.36,0:03:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh. It's smaller inside than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.90,0:03:31.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't compare it to a stadium!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.99,0:03:37.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't felt this kind of atmosphere in a while...\N since sixth grade, when I came to cheer you on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.08,0:03:41.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The dry air... the smell of dust...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.54,0:03:44.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Those seats over there are open.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.84,0:03:49.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, isn't that Arima?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.72,0:03:51.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's Arima-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.18,0:03:52.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Arima... you mean that pianist?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.97,0:03:53.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's all grown up now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.89,0:03:56.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You mean the youngest kid to\Never win the Saiki Competition?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.31,0:03:58.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I thought he was overseas?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.06,0:04:00.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's he doing at the Violin Competition?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.77,0:04:01.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Heyyy...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.39,0:04:02.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ex-celebrity!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.19,0:04:05.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The classical world sure is small!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.90,0:04:08.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you kept this from\Nme on purpose, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.94,0:04:10.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That we'd be going to hear her perform!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.78,0:04:12.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.20,0:04:16.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you knew about that, Kousei...\NYou wouldn't have come, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.66,0:04:19.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So I kept it on the\Ndown-low with all my might.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.25,0:04:29.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So the piano only\Nmakes you feel lousy, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.01,0:04:41.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs16}Towa Music Competition Committee Sponsor\NSecond Annual Towa Music Competition\NViolin - Middle School Division
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.64,0:04:39.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We will now begin the preliminary\Nround of the Towa Music Competition
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.43,0:04:41.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Violin Section for Middle-schoolers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.75,0:05:11.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Beethoven... Violin Sonata No. 9.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.72,0:05:14.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Kreutzer.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.93,0:05:18.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? He's asleep already?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.81,0:05:22.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's been a while since\NI heard a live performance.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.93,0:05:25.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What can I say...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.02,0:05:27.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm really starting to get goosebumps.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.87,0:05:42.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same song\Nover and over. Boring!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.08,0:05:45.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, that's the set piece. And\Nyou're the one who brought me here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.54,0:05:49.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But it's a pretty big turnout,\Nhuh? I'm a little surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.34,0:05:54.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is a newly-established major national\Ncompetition that's starting to get some notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.39,0:05:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The sponsors are kinda quirky.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.20,0:06:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, the set piece for the preliminary round\N would be Bach or Paganini numbers, played solo,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.85,0:06:05.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Towa Hall
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.60,0:06:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but in this contest, every number\Nfeatures an accompanist. That's pretty rare.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.02,0:06:12.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The winner gets the right to play on a\NGuarneri owned by the sponsors in a recital.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.28,0:06:15.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Guar...neri? Kabanini?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.45,0:06:21.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's off.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.71,0:06:28.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is it just me or does he stink?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.59,0:06:35.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You got this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.13,0:06:37.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You got this!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.94,0:06:52.44,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kazuhiro Oyama\NUmena Middle School
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.73,0:06:52.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that was too bad. And\Nhe started off so well, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.94,0:06:54.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He made two or three mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.69,0:06:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is he one of Mr. Sato's students?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.90,0:06:58.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.24,0:07:02.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Midway through, he started flailing\Nwith his bow. Guess he panicked.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.91,0:07:04.58,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Head Judge
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.20,0:07:09.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Still, what consistency. That was raw, but\Nthe overall level was high. He played it well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.25,0:07:11.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're absolutely right, Mr. Kazama!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.96,0:07:19.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, it got interesting after he messed up.\NAt this rate I'm going to fall asleep.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.34,0:07:21.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now, then, who's next?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.26,0:07:23.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Kao-chan's up next!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.89,0:07:26.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wake up, Watari!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.06,0:07:34.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, crap, I messed up...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.91,0:07:46.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Kao-chan looks so pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.91,0:07:46.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- I've been waiting for this, yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.88,0:08:01.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is making me nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.80,0:08:04.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My music...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.56,0:08:07.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Will it reach them?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.52,0:08:13.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Elohim, Essaim... Elohim, Essaim... I implore you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.67,0:08:35.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.03,0:09:44.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.07,0:09:48.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is the same song, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.88,0:10:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No question, it's the\Nset piece, the Kreutzer.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.46,0:10:02.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.69,0:10:19.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is blasphemy! Both the tempo\Nand the dynamics are all over the place!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.86,0:10:23.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's even ignoring the pianist\Nand going off on her own!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.11,0:10:26.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She might as well be picking\Na fight with the composer!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.79,0:10:37.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's the Kreutzer... but this\Npiece is no longer Beethoven's.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.96,0:10:40.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This piece...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.42,0:10:44.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's no denying that she owns it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.44,0:11:04.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's ultra-violent, her personality blows,\Nand she leaves the worst impression.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.78,0:11:06.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.42,0:11:29.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.23,0:11:45.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kao-chan, you're gorgeous!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.73,0:11:47.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kaori-chan, you're the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.40,0:11:51.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Aha, now that was stunning.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.99,0:11:55.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}An overwhelming personality,\Nrefusing to blindly obey the composer.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.58,0:11:57.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Though I'm sure it's\Nnot Mr. Kazama's cup of tea...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.91,0:11:59.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,During a serious competition!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.08,0:12:03.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What she has is on\Na whole different level.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.96,0:12:06.21,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kaori Miyazono\NSumitani Junior Highschool\N[Piano: Satomi Sakakibara]\NPrevious Awards: None
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.08,0:12:05.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How on earth is this girl not famous?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.47,0:12:23.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is amazing. They're still buzzing about her.\NIt's like a concert venue! You think she'll win?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.02,0:12:25.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What? Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.19,0:12:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But what a shame.\NWhat a crying shame.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.40,0:12:30.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is a competition, after all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.99,0:12:35.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way she'll win or\Neven place. Too many deductions.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.12,0:12:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not playing the way the\Nscore's written is a total taboo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.20,0:12:41.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But why? You saw how everyone loved it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.67,0:12:45.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I could see it if this were a recital,\Nbut no way in a competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.04,0:12:50.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But... I'm sure... That's\Nprobably not what she's seeking.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.63,0:12:54.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder how she can seem so\Nhappy while she's performing?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.51,0:13:01.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We will now take a fifteen-minute break.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.60,0:13:04.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That No. 4 was totally awesome, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.11,0:13:04.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is what she did allowed?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.95,0:13:06.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You mean Kaori Miyazono, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.11,0:13:07.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I even know her name now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.17,0:13:08.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'm a fan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.78,0:13:10.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about a huge impact!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.19,0:13:11.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.74,0:13:16.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing! They're all talking about Kao-chan.\NWell, she was really cool, wasn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.91,0:13:20.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't it like we were at a concert?\NShe was the only one I could stay awake for.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.54,0:13:22.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was beyond lame of you\Nto snooze from the get-go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.91,0:13:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I couldn't help it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.46,0:13:26.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.50,0:13:28.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um... Here...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.96,0:13:29.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Flowers for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.95,0:13:31.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We were so moved!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.37,0:13:33.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, they're so pretty! Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.84,0:13:38.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Ms. Miyazono. We'll be posting the result\N thirty minutes after the panel's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.64,0:13:40.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, don't mind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.64,0:13:43.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because I really don't\Ncare about that stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.10,0:13:47.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It means nothing unless you come in first.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.23,0:13:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kao-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.40,0:13:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tsubaki-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.20,0:13:55.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bye now. Thanks for the flowers!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.99,0:13:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.29,0:14:07.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The violinist who just finished performing...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.04,0:14:11.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Comes running towards\Nthose who await her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.01,0:14:14.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Weaving through the crowd...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.38,0:14:16.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Flowers in her arms...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.55,0:14:19.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's just like...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.10,0:14:22.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...a scene out of a movie...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.56,0:14:29.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That was awesome! You were so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.66,0:14:31.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.02,0:14:32.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.15,0:14:34.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Friend A!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.94,0:14:34.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, one sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.32,0:14:34.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.20,0:14:36.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.45,0:14:38.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What did you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.53,0:14:40.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? M-Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.45,0:14:42.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't I amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.45,0:14:44.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... See...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.75,0:14:47.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What... did you... think?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.54,0:14:52.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... Um... Not bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.18,0:15:00.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen anyone\Nget flowers after the prelims.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.18,0:15:04.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not only that, but you\Ndon't even know them, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.27,0:15:08.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They couldn't have known to\Nbring them, so for those girls...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.82,0:15:13.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,hearing your performance, then\Nrushing out to buy flowers to give to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.36,0:15:15.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It must've been an unforgettable day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.86,0:15:20.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think it was that kind of performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.83,0:15:26.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How do you like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.54,0:15:30.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's just like...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.33,0:15:32.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...a scene out of a movie.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.34,0:15:38.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Although I only played Friend A.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.14,0:15:44.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We will now be announcing the names of the\Ncontestants who cleared the preliminaries.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.52,0:15:46.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I see my name!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.85,0:15:48.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? No. 8 didn't make it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.52,0:15:49.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's my name!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.44,0:15:51.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna take a picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.60,0:15:53.36,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Passed First Preliminaries
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.19,0:15:53.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chie-chan, I see your name. Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.36,0:15:58.52,Grab,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Audience Choice: Kaori Miyazono
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.61,0:15:57.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Audience Award winner\Nmakes it to the second round, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.87,0:16:09.37,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Music Preparation Room
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.89,0:16:29.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Watari?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.56,0:16:30.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Man, you gave me a heart attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.89,0:16:33.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You weren't in the nurse's\Noffice, so I came to find you,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.07,0:16:36.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and you're passed out on the\Nfloor! I thought you were dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.57,0:16:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Arima?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.90,0:16:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Use this to ice the spot\Nwhere you got clobbered.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.20,0:16:43.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.41,0:16:47.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So? What were you up to, ditching\Nclass and screaming bloody murder?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.08,0:16:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing... I was just clearing my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.58,0:16:55.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you're acting pretty strange\Ntoday. Even more spaced out than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.42,0:17:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Could it be that you... You were\Nthinking about a girl you like, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.30,0:17:02.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Where did that come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.38,0:17:05.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That pretty much defines the\Nidle thoughts of adolescence, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.51,0:17:09.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Was it the timely Kaori-chan? Hey,\NI get it. She was so darned cute, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.77,0:17:13.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Never in a million years\Nand you know it! Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.60,0:17:14.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.98,0:17:17.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're in a supporting role. Kao-chan...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.78,0:17:21.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She likes you, Watari.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.20,0:17:24.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No way would she ever like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.91,0:17:28.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But that doesn't make any difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.87,0:17:33.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's only natural for the girl you're crushing\Non to be in love with someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.62,0:17:35.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Since you're in love with her,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.08,0:17:37.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,she sparkles in your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.46,0:17:40.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's why people fall so irrationally in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.47,0:17:45.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think I kind of get why you're\Nsuch a chick-magnet, Watari.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.80,0:17:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You bet. There are plenty\Nof girls that I like!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.68,0:17:50.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But for me, it's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.68,0:17:52.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.81,0:17:56.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whether or not it's impossible,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.44,0:17:58.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,the girl will let you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.65,0:18:01.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You give good advice, Watari.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.94,0:18:03.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't I though?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.15,0:18:05.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you! Watari!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.36,0:18:07.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You made Keiko cry again, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.70,0:18:09.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,C-Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.03,0:18:10.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, calm down?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.54,0:18:13.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was gonna ditch practice today\Nand go home with Keiko-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.75,0:18:15.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing as I've neglected her for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.54,0:18:18.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're awful, after all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.46,0:18:22.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Watari's right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.34,0:18:26.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm not myself today. I'm out of here...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.77,0:18:36.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Before I know it...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.56,0:18:39.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Against a screen of bright red clouds...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.27,0:18:42.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I hear the refrain against the\Nblack curtain of my closed eyes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.74,0:18:46.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Over and over... Again and again...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.82,0:18:49.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Again and again...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.37,0:18:52.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And every time, my heart...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.08,0:18:58.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's like what my mother\Nleft me scatters away...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.50,0:19:04.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to hear it again, yet I\Ndon't want to hear it again...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.05,0:19:08.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}One more time...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.85,0:19:13.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to see her,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.35,0:19:16.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}yet I don't want to see her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.40,0:19:23.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This kind of feeling...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.53,0:19:25.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What was it called again?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.32,0:19:33.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What do you call this\Nkind of feeling again?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.16,0:19:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Friend A.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.41,0:19:40.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You exist inside spring.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.09,0:19:49.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's wearing our school uniform.\NSo you really are a student here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.22,0:19:51.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you staring at?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.39,0:19:54.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You were gonna sneak\Nanother shot, weren't you? Pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.85,0:19:56.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I would never, and I didn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.31,0:19:58.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Liar! You're gonna spread\Nit all over the internet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.52,0:20:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I won't, I won't!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.65,0:20:03.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, never mind. It'll only make\Nmy popularity explode anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.77,0:20:05.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Talk about over-confident...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.24,0:20:08.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, where's Watari-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.74,0:20:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Watari?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.99,0:20:12.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want to scare him, so I'm lying in wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.49,0:20:17.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was gonna ditch practice today\Nand go home with Keiko-chan!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.08,0:20:20.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Think he'll be here soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.96,0:20:25.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, no sign of him\Nshowing up at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.09,0:20:27.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Watari's...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.38,0:20:30.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's still in practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.43,0:20:32.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.26,0:20:36.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.68,0:20:41.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then maybe I'll go take a\Npeek at the soccer team.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.77,0:20:43.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.56,0:20:45.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They've got their summer\Ntournament coming up, see!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.86,0:20:48.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if you should\Nbarge in on practice...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.78,0:20:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Right! I don't\Nthink it's a good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.12,0:20:53.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Watari's quite nervous about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.62,0:20:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, you do have a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.25,0:21:01.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I disrupt him, he'll hate me, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.75,0:21:08.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm appointing you as his substitute!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.95,0:21:19.97,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Friend A
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.97,0:21:19.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.92,0:22:38.82,Next,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 3\NInside Spring
